<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.2.6">
<l>ēviṟ ṟucceyvā ṉēṉṟetirn tuvanta mallarai</l>
<l>cāvat takarttacān taṇitōḷ caturaṉ malai</l>
<l>yāvat taṉameṉ ṟamarar kaḷumnaṉ muṉivaruñ</l>
<l>cēvit tirukkun teṉtiru māliruñ cōlaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of him with four arms annointed with sandal paste</l>
<l rend="indent">who smashed the wrestlers who came against [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">in accordance with [the wishes of] he who gave the orders,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [they] died,</l>
<l>is Tirumāliruñcōlai in the South where immortals and good sages</l>
<l rend="indent">serve [him], saying “Succor in [times of] adversity”.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
